001package io.jstach.rainbowgum;
002
003import java.net.URI;
004import java.util.NoSuchElementException;
005
006import org.eclipse.jdt.annotation.Nullable;
007
008import io.jstach.rainbowgum.LogProperty.Result;
009
010/**
011 * Log LogProvider Source.
012 */
013public sealed interface LogProviderRef {
014
015        /**
016         * URI of the log provider.
017         * @return uri not <code>null</code>.
018         */
019        URI uri();
020
021        /**
022         * Property key from where the URI came from or <code>null</code>.
023         * @return property key.
024         */
025        @Nullable
026        String keyOrNull();
027
028        /**
029         * Creates a log provider ref from URI.
030         * @param uri uri.
031         * @return ref.
032         */
033        public static LogProviderRef of(URI uri) {
034                return new DefaultLogProviderRef(uri, null);
035        }
036
037        /**
038         * Create a provider ref from a property result.
039         * @param property successful URI result.
040         * @return provider ref.
041         */
042        public static LogProviderRef of(Result.Success<? extends URI> property) {
043                return new DefaultLogProviderRef(property.value(), property.key());
044        }
045
046        /**
047         * Creates a log provider ref from URI.
048         * @param uri uri.
049         * @param key property key where URI came from.
050         * @return ref.
051         */
052        public static LogProviderRef of(URI uri, @Nullable String key) {
053                return new DefaultLogProviderRef(uri, key);
054        }
055
056        /**
057         * Thrown if a provider could not be found for the ref.
058         */
059        public static class NotFoundException extends NoSuchElementException {
060
061                private static final long serialVersionUID = 5484668688480940159L;
062
063                NotFoundException(String s) {
064                        super(s);
065                        // TODO Auto-generated constructor stub
066                }
067
068        }
069
070}
071
072record DefaultLogProviderRef(URI uri, @Nullable String keyOrNull) implements LogProviderRef {
073}
